@startuml
title make dev-up Sequence

actor Developer
participant "make dev-up" as Make
participant "scripts/dev/up.sh" as Script
participant Helm
participant "k3s API" as K8s
participant "Kafka Pods" as Kafka

Developer -> Make : make dev-up
Make -> Script : bash scripts/dev/up.sh
Script -> Helm : helm upgrade --install kafka
Helm -> K8s : create namespace + release resources
K8s -> Kafka : schedule controller and broker
Kafka --> Developer : kafka.kafka.svc.cluster.local:9092

@enduml
